title: Basilico Crouch End
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Italian, Delivery, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. One of several branches making Italian pizzas, cooked in traditional wood fired ovens, and delivered to your door. Offers vegan cheese and has two vegan pizzas on the menu or you can make your own. Gluten free bases available too.
